utservice` 和 `frontend` 也出现高延迟和错误。\n\n### 输出结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio and rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart 延迟从 1952ms 增加到 1536468ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder 延迟从 148672ms 增加到 547015ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 下一步建议\n1. **检查 `cartservice` 的健康状态**，确认是否存在资源瓶颈或代码逻辑问题。\n2. **检查 `redis` 服务**，因为 `cartservice` 依赖 Redis，可能存在 Redis 性能问题。\n3. **监控网络延迟**，尤其是 `cartservice` 与其他服务之间的通信。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "009be6db-313", "component": "cartservice", "reason": "FailedPrecondition and Can't access cart storage errors causing rrt_max spike from 1952ms to 1536468ms", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LogSearch(cartservice)", "observation": "Found FailedPrecondition errors: Can't access cart storage in cartservice logs"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LoadMetrics(cartservice)", "observation": "rrt_max increased from 1952ms to 1536468ms in cartservice operations"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(009be6db-313)", "observation": "checkoutservice->cartservice calls show 600x latency increase"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
